well guys it was my bday yesterday n omg was it great! well it started in the morning wen i woke up my mom n sis had put my gifts in my room w/ ballons(i got pants a belt n money!) . it was so nice! i love u guys! and then i got ready n my dad called we talked n then i went to school, at school i went to tutor(i was tutoring anissa!) n roman called n i was like omg! yay! i miss you! n then jenni called n i was like yay! n thnx for the gift card i love it n we gotta get out matching polos ne ways that was great!i love u two! lol n i was wearing a kiss me its my bday pin so ppl were kissing me .. n then tutoring was over so then i go down to c my frinds n they all hug me n kiss me !i love u guys! and Cindy, joelle, and danielle made me cakes (u guys r awesome) and carly , melody and andrea gave me their present .. i love it u guys i just wish i could wear it! soon i will !i love u all! and macky! gave me my first hug in the morning, she jumped on me n it was a good 5 seconds hug! lol.. i love u macky!! (man theres alot of love going on in here XD lol) ne ways were was i oh right so then we hug n kiss n more hugs n more kisses and then i get my stuff w/ the help of astrid n bruss (thnx guys i love u guys two!) n we go to first period n we listened to love songs etc and then they sang me happy bday . n then in second per we colored (with glue and chalk, it was fun!) and then i went o 3rd n jenni bruss joe n i all talked n we did our ws n then bruss n i studied a bit for our quix in math . then in 4th per i took my quiz then in 5th per i did my programs n more huggs n more happy bdays! (how exciting! i love it). then in 6th i got to give alisha the heimlich manouver. lol she wasnt choking but we had to practice for our test which was today n i passed . im sorry alisha if it hurt too much i love u!then i met up with amber n she n i got a ride home from my mom because i asked her if she could help me carry one of my cakes and then we talked about stuff because i didnt get to c her in the morning so that aniother reason y i asked her to come .. we talk about a whole mess of random stuff lol i love u amber! and then i went home n opened my presents and ate sum cake n drank sum milk did my hw on the fone w/ bruss n then wen out to dinner . me n my fam went to on the border adn i say andrea from my photo class there adn she was our hostes neways then my sis n i ate soo much tortilla chips w/ spicy dip yummy  they were soo good then i ordered a beef burrito , that was good too with cheese beans n rice yumm! n then we left and came home and during the day a lot of ppl called my cell lets c : ashley, carlos, danielle and leilani(which i didnt get to speak to them), roman again, my grandmother , and them my mosm friend monica. i love u all! so then i went to sleep and today was an early release so it was ok math test killed y day but its all good and then after school i went to the fals w/ jenni and alisha(i love u guys) and we ate crepes (caesar chicken) yummy! and then we went to c beauty shop that was funny n then we walked around .. guys remeeber we gota deside a color for the polos. n then we has popcorn n then we had starbucks yummy!X2.. lol n then i got home did hw n talked on the fone to bruss. these two days have been great! oh n this saturday im going to clean up the rickenbaucher beach with my friends (thats gonna be great!).. well thats been my bday! it was fun! 
p.s.- i love u jenni c.!
p.p.s- hey guys get my new s/n cuz i 4got the password to my old one.. lol .. yes i forgot it oh well so the new one is fotosestas311

hey well today was great i went to the beach w/ melody and my family n relatives from colombia . it was fun .. we had a great time we stayed in the beach the whole day .. then me n melody say a news reporter*telemundo* n we were curious so we asked wut they were filming for n he said it was about how the beach was n he asked if we wanted to b in it .. n we were like ok so we were askked how the beach was n if it was nice to be in it .. so melody said it was nice n i said it was great the water was nice n calm. yea it was fun especialy since it was in spanish melody couldnt answer much lol.. then we ate at burger king .. then i went home jumped in puddles w/ my dog n got wet. then i took a shower n went to carlos's house we listened to music n watched tv it was fun lol he has the same room i have lol *same type of apartments*.. we watched i love the 90's; 1995. n listened to music. then iw ent home n now im here .. well g2g byes ttyl cya later peace

hey everyone, well today i went to dadeland mall n hung out w/ my sis dad n grandma, we walked n ate at cheesecake factory, we talked n had a blast, then i went home n like at 430 carlos, his family n i went to el doral to try to go to the venezuelan festival .. but it was too smoky n the entrance was expensive so instead we went bowling, it was funny . n there i saw ahsley n karen from glades, then we decided to go to eat n we ate at burger king .. then i got home n now i here .. wel g2g byes ttyl .. awesome day.. peace

hey everyone, guess what? well today i went to volunteer at baptist, i got very tired , then my mom piked me up early so we could go to the DMV .. n yes i took the learners permit test .. n yes I PASSED! YAY! well yea thats it .. well g2g eat byes ttyl cya

hey everyone, well its been a while .. but i got great events to tell u all. first school enede n i did good on my report card , n i got the classes i wanted.. ok got that over w/ .. now my friends heidi, hannah, ana, and georgis all moved to differnt states .. omg ima miss them so much .. then i had to go on vacation it was fun we drove up to jacksonville n hung out with our friends from colombia , we had a great time . then we took another road trip to charleston , sc it was great we went to the beach n toured around town .. its really a great place .. then we went bak to jacksonville n hung out for a few more days n then headed out for daytona beach .. it was great there too we hung out in the hotel most of the time .. since it was on the beach so we would go to the beach n then pool eat n then bak in the pool. great! o n they had a kareoke night n i danced the macarena n the chiken dance .. it was a blast .. then we had to say goodbye to our friends n head down to miami.. then my sis n i just stayed at home n played games n went to the pool.. then on 4th of july it was great i met up w/ joelle n jess n we walked around baptist hospital's lake n just talked n made fools out of our selves... or maybe that was just me lol . then jess called her friend carlos to meet w/ us n then we all sat on the grass to eat n talk , we had a great time . n i second wat joelle said " carlos was really nice , n for the record hes NOT fat!" . then we all heared a big boom in an instant we all scattered cuz we had to be with our parents wen the fireworks began .. turns out the boom wasnt a firework lol .. so we ran for nothing .. o well then i met up w/ my mom n carly melody n andrea we sat n watched the fireworks .. they were really nice. lots of colors n booms n sparkles. then it ended n we decided to go home wen we got in our car some lade starts going pshyco n backs up in to our car .. as she comes out shes telling us we moved the car forward .. good thing the card just got a minor dent .. but the lady was lieing right to our faces .. i was soo pissed! then we got home n i could fall asleep so i went to talk to my sis .. she couldnt fall asleep either .. we talked n then fell asleep . then today i went to go play dodgeball at church with a few friends n one of them get hurt .. luky for the rest of us she was our ride .. so we had to take the bus , just dandy. and now i here chatting online .. n i send a big huge hug to my friend joelle cuz ur awesome n i love u!
